==事故==
1947年2月2日，一列特快列車與一列本地列車在本站相撞<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.railwaysarchive.co.uk/documents/MoT_Gidea1947.pdf |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-01-04 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924121053/http://www.railwaysarchive.co.uk/documents/MoT_Gidea1947.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，導致7人喪生，45人因受傷而住院治療<ref name=Earnshaw7>{{cite book |last=Earnshaw |first=Alan |title=Trains in Trouble: Vol. 7 |year=1991 |publisher=Atlantic Books |location=Penryn |isbn=0-906899-50-8 |page=30 }}</ref>
